@startuml ContractorPro Demo Flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor transparent

title **ContractorPro - Automation Demo**

actor Contractor
actor Client
database System

== Quote Phase ==
Contractor -> System : Create Job (with client email)
Contractor -> System : Create Estimate
System -> Client : **AUTO: Professional Quote Email**
Client -> Contractor : Approve Project

== Construction Phase ==
note over System : **Photo → Email Automation**

Contractor -> System : Upload Photo + 25% Milestone
System -> Client : **AUTO: "25% Complete - Demo Done"**

Contractor -> System : Upload Photo + 50% Milestone  
System -> Client : **AUTO: "50% Complete - Framing"**

Contractor -> System : Upload Photo + 75% Milestone
System -> Client : **AUTO: "75% Complete - Finishing"**

Contractor -> System : Upload Photo + 100% Milestone
System -> Client : **AUTO: "Project Complete!"**

note right of System
**Key Automation:**
• Photo upload triggers email
• Professional messaging
• Client stays informed
• No manual updates needed
end note

@enduml